{"tid":731734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尖嘴珠寶行2千萬元劫案 27歲男子被捕","createTime":"2018-07-06T12:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T12:57:59.000Z","uid":193407,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f7c78e3807667da57cd90461225264c4d1766e","tid":731734,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180706/58407869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180706%2F58407869&d=G23sMlIDbip8kPqvS0Sf2NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8ca071bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180706%2F58407869&h=50d22b5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180706/58407869</a><br />\n<br />\n鐵鎚幫「7.1」劫尖沙嘴海防道珠寶行，掠去2,350萬元名錶及手鏈( <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IJSPGv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IJSPGv&d=G23sMlIDbip8kPqvS0Sf2NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=679747d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IJSPGv</a> )，警方經過多日追查，在屯門拘捕一名27歲男子，稍後將交代案情。<br />\n<br />\n案發於周日(7月1日) 早上10時45分，3名戴帽及口罩的匪徒，分別持伸縮棍、利刀及鐵鎚衝進海防道「名人鐘錶珠寶」，以廣東話大叫「唔好郁，打劫！」其間一名男店員正在低頭「篤手機」，被匪徒誤會報警求助，當場摑面威嚇，最後閃電擸走一批總值約2,350萬元的名錶及手鏈。事發個多小時後，歹徒駕乘的私家車，被棄於新田米埔新村放火焚燒，毀滅證據。"},{"pid":"77f85d882e829e2015f8276ca15bfdfdcb4341b0","tid":731734,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f7c78e3807667da57cd90461225264c4d1766e","tid":731734,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces